title: Neff Invades Coachella 2012
description: Neff Headwear hits the road for Coachella 2012. From pool parties to the festival to the after parties, Neff made their presence know. Check out all the sick Neff caps, watches and sunglasses. Neff watched Calvin Harris, David Guetta, Kaskade, AVICII, Snoop Dogg and the Tupac Hologram from front row. Be sure to check www.neffheadwear.com for the complete blog post on our Coachella 2012 trip.
